MadeInG.create!([
  {content_pl: "<p>Wysokiej klasy projekt architektoniczny, najlepsze marki z sektora premium w jednym koncepcie oraz inne korzyści płynące z bycia częścią sieci franczyzowej – to gwarancja sukcesu.</p>", img_file_name: "2.jpg", img_content_type: "image/jpeg", img_file_size: 574891, img_updated_at: "2015-07-15 21:28:25", content_en: "<p>High quality architectural design, the best brands of premium sector in one concept and other benefits of being part of a franchise network – this is a guarantee of success. </p>", content_it: "<p>I nostri prestigiosi marchi all’interno di un design architettonico di alta classe rappresentano quanto di meglio il mercato del franchising possa offrire oggi.</p>"},
  {content_pl: "<p>Concept Made in G oraz Made in G Accessories to unikalny projekt salon&oacute;w multimarkowych. Rozwijany w formule franczyzy, skupia brandy znajdujące się w potrfolio GPoland i jest odpowiedzią na zapotrzebowanie polskiego rynku.</p>", img_file_name: "1.jpg", img_content_type: "image/jpeg", img_file_size: 333652, img_updated_at: "2015-07-15 21:27:52", content_en: "<p>Made in G and Made in G Accessories concept is an unique multibrand store project. Developed in the formula of the franchise, this project focuses brands which are included in GPOLAND potrfolio and responds to the needs of the Polish market.</p>", content_it: "<p>Il concetto Made In G e Made in G Accessories &egrave; un esclusivo progetto in franchising di boutique multimarca.</p>"}
])
