Showroom.create!([
  {content_pl: "<p>Do dyspozycji stylist&oacute;w magazyn&oacute;w, program&oacute;w telewizyjnych i celebryt&oacute;w jest r&oacute;wnież showroom prasowy.</p>", img_file_name: "8.jpg", img_content_type: "image/jpeg", img_file_size: 397965, img_updated_at: "2015-07-15 21:30:40", content_en: "<p>In addition to the individual brands corners, GPoland has also the press showroom, which is visited every day by stylists from the magazines, TV shows and celebrities.</p>", content_it: "<p>Oltre ai spazi dedicati ai singoli brand, GPoland offre alla stampa uno showroom visitato ogni giorno da stilisti di riviste specializzate, di programmi televisivi e da celebrit&agrave; del mondo dello spettacolo.</p>"},
  {content_pl: "<h2>SHOWROOM GPOLAND</h2>\r\n<p>BlueCity, Al. Jerozolimskie 179<br /> 02-222 Warszawa<br /> Poziom +2, Blue Office 3<br /> tel./fax: 22 824 34 41<br /> gpoland@gpoland.com.pl</p>", img_file_name: "9.JPG", img_content_type: "image/jpeg", img_file_size: 481383, img_updated_at: "2015-07-15 21:30:56", content_en: "<h2>Showroom GPoland</h2>\r\n<p>BlueCity, Al. Jerozolimskie 179<br /> 02-222 Warsaw<br /> Level 2, Blue Office 3<br /> tel./fax: 22 824 34 41<br /> gpoland@gpoland.com.pl</p>", content_it: "<h2>Showroom GPoland</h2>\r\n<p>BlueCity, Al. Jerozolimskie 179<br /> 02-222 Varsavia<br /> II piano, Blue Office 3<br /> tel./fax: 22 824 34 41<br /> gpoland@gpoland.com.pl</p>"},
  {content_pl: "<p>Showroom Gpoland to idealne miejsce dla wielbicieli mody. Na blisko 5000 metr&oacute;w kwadratowych agencja realizuje zam&oacute;wienia handlowe wsp&oacute;lnie z Partnerami z całej Polski. Komfortowe warunki oraz profesjonalne doradztwo gwarantują powodzenie kontraktacji.</p>", img_file_name: "4.JPG", img_content_type: "image/jpeg", img_file_size: 289835, img_updated_at: "2015-07-15 21:30:06", content_en: "<p>Gpoland Showroom is the perfect place for admirers of fashion. On nearly two thousand square metres our agency conducts orders with Partners from all over Poland. Comfortable conditions and professional consulting guarantee success in contracting.</p>", content_it: "<p>Lo Showroom GPoland si articola su quasi 2000 mq di esposizione ed &egrave; il luogo ideale per gli amanti della moda. Qui accogliamo i nostri Partner commerciali provenienti da tutta la Polonia. Eccellenti condizioni e consulenza professionale garantiscono un ottimo risultato dal punto di vista commerciale.</p>"}
])
